posting_body: ['162 Neponset St  Norwood, MA  02062', '$2700.00 / Month', '---------------------------', 'Interested in this property?', 'Reply to this listing for more information.', '---------------------------', 'Property Details:', '3 BEDROOMS | 2.5 BATHROOMS', 'Great property with excellent location around Boston.', 'Located 1 mile off 95, .5 miles from route 1 South, and a mile from the Norwood train station.', ' Also located in between the popular Legacy Place and Foxboro Place shopping centers.', ' It has been a great house to live at while working in and around the city.', ' Everything is well maintained and the house has a nice open concept downstairs.', ' 2 garages located underneath the house, as well as an unfinished basement used for a fitness area.', ' Walking distance to Norwood Center, Calahan Elementry School and Xaverian Brothers High School.', ' Looking for the right renters to enjoy a great house.', 'Willing to discuss length of stay and school situations, very flexible about what people may need.', ' Feel free to contact anytime to set up a showing and a possible move in date of Sept 1st.', '***Cats, Small Dogs, Large Dogs Allowed***', 'Property Type:', 'Single Family', 'Lease Terms:', '$2700.00/Month', '$1000.00 Deposit', 'Lease Length:', 'One Year', 'Available:', '09/01/2022', 'Unit Amenities:', 'Dishwasher', 'Freezer', 'Dryer', 'Garbage Disposal', 'Oven', 'Microwave', 'Refrigerator', 'Washer', 'Building Amenities:', 'On Site Laundry', 'Wired For Internet', 'Garage', 'Cable Ready', 'Accessibility Features', 'Fenced Yard', 'Fireplace', 'Lawn', 'Near Parks', '---------------------------', 'Interested in this property?', 'Reply to this listing for more information.']
